16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
18 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 23 of Title 22, unless there is
19 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
20 No court nor other state entity shall contract with a private
21 debt collector or private debt collection agency to collect
22 outstanding criminal fines, fees, costs, or restitution of any
23 individual.
